EGM_Bonus_Amount, Seconds_Played, Points_Earned, Casino_Cash_Earned, Casino_Location, EGM_Denomination, Gaming_Activity_Code, Sub_Game_Code, Table_Area, Table_Minimum_Bet, Table_Limit, Table_Level, Program_Number, Program_Chip_Type, Rating_Status, SuperId, DealerId, EGMStroke, GameWins, JnktRatingFlg, ProgCompValEarned, TblChipsIn, TblCheqIn, TblCshIn, Limit_Hit_Time, Limit_Hit_Date, Limit_Hit_Type, Anc_Card_Legacy_Patron_Id, DeptNum, GrossRev, NetRev, PointEarningRatio, RatingType, CashlessIn, ETGTerminalNumber, F_RATINGID, F_RATINGHOURID, F_LEGACYPATRONID FROM ( SELECT S_GamingRating.Legacy_Patron_Id, S_GamingRating.Property_Location_Number, S_GamingRating.RatingId, S_GamingRating.Gaming_Date, S_GamingRating.Start_Time, S_GamingRating.End_Time, S_GamingRating.Turnover, S_GamingRating.Buy_In, S_GamingRating.Average_Bet, S_GamingRating.Actual_Win, S_GamingRating.Theoretical_Win, S_GamingRating.EGM_Jackpot_Amount, S_GamingRating.EGM_Bonus_Amount, S_GamingRating.Seconds_Played, S_GamingRating.Points_Earned, S_GamingRating.Casino_Cash_Earned, S_GamingRating.Casino_Location, S_GamingRating.EGM_Denomination, S_GamingRating.Gaming_Activity_Code, S_GamingRating.Sub_Game_Code, S_GamingRating.Table_Area, S_GamingRating.Table_Minimum_Bet, S_GamingRating.Table_Limit, S_GamingRating.Table_Level, S_GamingRating.Program_Number, S_GamingRating.Program_Chip_Type, S_GamingRating.Rating_Status, S_GamingRating.SuperId, S_GamingRating.DealerId, S_GamingRating.EGMStroke, S_GamingRating.GameWins, S_GamingRating.JnktRatingFlg, S_GamingRating.ProgCompValEarned, S_GamingRating.TblChipsIn, S_GamingRating.TblCheqIn, S_GamingRating.TblCshIn, S_GamingRating.Limit_Hit_Time, S_GamingRating.Limit_Hit_Date, S_GamingRating.Limit_Hit_Type, S_GamingRating.Anc_Card_Legacy_Patron_Id, S_GamingRating.DeptNum, S_GamingRating.GrossRev, S_GamingRating.NetRev, S_GamingRating.PointEarningRatio, S_GamingRating.RatingType, S_GamingRating.CashlessIn, --//included cashlessin field on 080724 S_GamingRating.ETGTerminalNumber, --//included ETGTerminalNumber field on 170625 /*D_PATRON.PATRONID, D_PATRON.DOB, ANC_PATRON.PATRONID,*/ F_GAMINGRATING.RATINGID F_RATINGID, F_GAMINGRATING.RATINGHOURID F_RATINGHOURID, F_GAMINGRATING.LEGACYPATRONID F_LEGACYPATRONID, --in case of duplicate ratings order of priority is 1. Ratings re-supplied from Syco(i.e RejectETLJobDtlId is null), 2.The latest reject record (sourced from reject table) rank() over (partition by S_GamingRating.RatingId,S_GamingRating.Legacy_Patron_Id order by (case when S_GamingRating.RejectETLJobDtlId is null then 1 else 0 end) desc, S_GamingRating.RejectETLJobDtlId desc) as rnk FROM S_GamingRating /*LEFT OUTER JOIN D_PATRON ON ( D_PATRON.LEGACYPATRONIDCHAR = S_GamingRating.Legacy_Patron_Id AND D_PATRON.SiteID = $$SiteID AND convert(date, S_GamingRating.Gaming_Date, 103) >= D_PATRON.BEGEFFDT AND ( convert(date, S_GamingRating.Gaming_Date, 103) <= D_PATRON.ENDEFFDT OR D_PATRON.ENDEFFDT IS NULL) ) LEFT OUTER JOIN D_PATRON ANC_PATRON ON ANC_PATRON.LEGACYPATRONIDCHAR = S_GamingRating.Anc_Card_Legacy_Patron_Id AND ANC_PATRON.SiteID = $$SiteID AND convert(date, S_GamingRating.Gaming_Date, 103) >= ANC_PATRON.BEGEFFDT AND ( convert(date, S_GamingRating.Gaming_Date, 103) <= ANC_PATRON.ENDEFFDT OR ANC_PATRON.ENDEFFDT IS NULL)*/ LEFT OUTER JOIN F_GamingRating ON F_GamingRating.RatingID=convert(integer, S_GamingRating.RatingID) and F_GamingRating.legacypatronid=convert(integer, S_GamingRating.Legacy_patron_id) and F_GamingRating.SiteID=$$SiteID WHERE S_GamingRating.Property_Location_Number in $$Property_no_list ) ratings where rnk = 1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select min(j.JackpotTypeOrder) as JackpotProductTypeOrder, c.CasinoLocDetID as CasinoLocDetID, d.DayID as DayID from S_GamingRating s, D_CasinoLocationDet c, (select JkptStrucID, Case JkptTypCde when 'LKMYS' then 3 when 'CAMYS' then 3 when 'GLMYS' then 3 when 'STPRG' then 2 when 'HYPLK' then 1 when 'LKPRG' then 1 when 'STMYS' then 2 when 'CASCH' then 3 when 'LKSCH' then 3 else 8 end as JackpotTypeOrder from D_Jackpot_Structure) j, (select distinct a.jkptstrucid, a.casinolocdetid, a.terminallocationdetid, a.jkptconfigstartdyid, a.jkptconfigrtrddyid, a.SiteID from F_Jackpot_Configuration a) f, D_Day d where s.Property_Location_Number in $$Property_no_list and c.SiteID=$$SiteID and s.Casino_Location=c.CasinoLoc and c.LocTypCode='S' and c.CasinoLocDetID=f.CasinoLocDetID and convert(date, S.Gaming_Date, 103) =d.fulldt and d.dayid between f.JkptConfigStartDyID and f.JkptConfigRtrdDyID and f.JkptStrucID=j.JkptStrucID group by c.CasinoLocDetID, d.DayID order by c.CasinoLocDetID, d.DayID, JackpotProductTypeOrder --
